'''Madrid Chhṳ-chhṳ Thai-ho̍k''' ([[Sî-pân-ngà-ngî]]: Universidad Autónoma de Madrid) , vi [[Sî-pân-ngà]] sû-tû [[Madrid]] ke yit-ke kûng-li̍p thai-ho̍k, chhóng-kien yî 1968-ngièn. Chú káu-khî vi-yî Madrid pet-kau ke Cantoblanco. Madrid Chhṳ-chhṳ Thai-ho̍k he Sî-pân-ngà chui yû-miàng ke thai-ho̍k chṳ̂-yit, thi̍t-phe̍t he khì Fap-ho̍k-yen pí-káu vi tî-miàng.
